<span id="freeTextContainer11356242914179569880">Raymond Chandler meets Philip K. Dick? I didn&apos;t expect to like this odd near future neo-noir quite so much. If you like <i>Blade Runner</i>, <i>The Big Sleep</i>, and <i>Who Framed Roger Rabbit</i> you&apos;ll have to give this trippy novel a try. I&apos;m going to have to read more sci-fi noir and Jonathan Lethem in the future.<br/><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1554667070ra/27328855.gif' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/></span>
